title: The Free
text:
The Free were a German eurodance group from the 1990s. They were produced by Felix J. Gauder and Olaf Roberto Bossi.


== Members ==
1994–1995: Iris Trevisan
1995–1996: Ayla J.
1994–1999: Charles Simmons
